[0.000, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[2;46r\u001b8\r\u001b[46d\n\u001b[1;48r\u001b[45;1H; automatically after every output block.  This is equivalent to calling the\u001b[45;33H"]
[0.034, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[?1c\u001b[?25h\u001b[?0c"]
[0.001, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[2;46r\u001b8\r\u001b[46d\n\u001b[1;48r\u001b[45;1H; PHP function flush() after each and every call to print() or echo() and each\u001b[45;33H"]
[0.033, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[?1c\u001b[?25h\u001b[?0c"]
[0.001, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[2;46r\u001b8\r\u001b[46d\n\u001b[1;48r\u001b[45;1H; and every HTML block.  Turning this option on has serious performance\u001b[45;33H"]
