[0.000, "o", "\u001b7\u001b[2;46r\u001b8\r\u001b[46d\n\u001b[1;48r\u001b[45;1H; what PATH_INFO is.  For more information on PATH_INFO, see the cgi specs.  Setting\u001b[45;33H"]
